DESCRIPTION:Making Local Markets Downtown Bothell comes alive with creativi
	ty and community at the Making Local Markets on Saturday\, March 28\, 2026
	\, from 10 AM to 4 PM. This vibrant outdoor market showcases 100\\+ small\
	, local\, handmade businesses\, plus an array of delicious food trucks. St
	roll through the bustling streets\, discover unique finds\, and soak in th
	e lively atmosphere. With pet-friendly vibes\, free parking at City Hall\,
	 and plenty of great bars and restaurants nearby\, it's the perfect way to
	 spend a spring Saturday. Don't miss this celebration of local craftsmansh
	ip in the heart of Bothell!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detai
